com.rohitsood.urlybird.gui.search
Class SearchResultTableModel

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      com.rohitsood.urlybird.gui.search.SearchResultTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class SearchResultTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel

Holds the search result data in the TableModel. Tracks the record id, defines the column names and convenience methods. Table columns are defined which contain all data columns including record id.

Version:
1.1
Author:
Rohit Sood
